INSERT INTO users(
                    confirmed,
                    uuid,
                    username,
                    given_name,
                    family_name,
                    email,
                    password,
                    score,
                    location,
                    roaming
                )
                VALUES (
                    'TRUE',
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3,
                    $4,
                    $5,
                    $6,
                    $7,
                    $8,
                    $9
                )

WITH
            id_user
        AS
        (
            SELECT
                id
            FROM
                users
            WHERE
                uuid=$1
        ),
            id_extended
        AS
        (
            INSERT INTO
                extended_profiles
                (
                    user_id,
                    birthday,
                    gender,
                    sexual_orientation
                )
            VALUES
                (
                    (SELECT id FROM id_user),
                    $2,
                    $3,
                    $4
                )
            ON CONFLICT
                (
                    user_id
                )
            DO
                UPDATE
                SET
                    birthday=$2,
                    gender=$3,
                    sexual_orientation=$4
                WHERE
                    extended_profiles.user_id=(
                        SELECT id FROM id_user
                    )
            RETURNING
                id
            )
            UPDATE
                users
            SET
                extended_profile=(select id from id_extended)
            WHERE
                id=(
                    SELECT id FROM id_user
                );

WITH
            id_user
        AS
        (
            SELECT
                id
            FROM
                users
            WHERE
                uuid=$1
        ),
            id_extended
        AS
        (
            INSERT INTO
                extended_profiles
                (
                    user_id,
                    biography
                )
            VALUES
                (
                    (SELECT id FROM id_user),
                    $2
                )
            ON CONFLICT
                (
                    user_id
                )
            DO
                UPDATE
                SET
                    biography=$2
                WHERE
                    extended_profiles.user_id = (
                        SELECT id FROM id_user
                    )
            RETURNING
                id
        )
        UPDATE
            users
        SET
            extended_profile = (
                SELECT id FROM id_extended
            )
        WHERE
            id = ( 
                SELECT id FROM id_user
            );
